# ------------ phpUpdateSite ------------
# version	0.1
# author	hannes eilers
# --------------------------------------
#
# ---------------------------------------
# DESCRIPTION
# ---------------------------------------
phpUpdateSite is a simple php script to enable
api access to software update files.

It stores files for each version of a program
in a directory.

Using the api calls external programs can
request available update pages (one for each
program for example), available versions of
one page or files inside a version update
directory.

The external program can use the offered file
urls to download the files and use them for
any kind of update.

# ---------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# ---------------------------------------
Use these parameters of webserver page
request to get several information.
If you don't set a parameter all available
update pages are listed.

p	Use to show versions of a page.
	For example: update.php?p=HELP
	
lv	Use in combination with parameter p
	to get latest version number.
	For example: update.php?p=HELP&lv
	
l	Use in combination with parameter p
	to get latest version update files.
	For example: update.php?p=HELP&l

v	Use to show update files of version
	inside a page in combination with
	parameter p.
	For example: update.php?p=HELP&v=0.1

# ---------------------------------------